## Technical Requirements

- Single `page.tsx` file with all sections as individual components defined in the same file for simplicity
- All animations via Framer Motion — use `useInView` for scroll triggers and `AnimatePresence` for the loading screen
- Typewriter effect built with `useState` and `useEffect` — no external library
- Number counter animation built with Framer Motion `useMotionValue` and `useSpring`
- Ticker bar uses pure CSS `@keyframes` marquee animation — no JS
- Background grid or particle effect uses `<canvas>` with `requestAnimationFrame` or pure CSS — no Three.js
- Scanline overlay: a fixed `::before` pseudo-element on the body with a repeating linear gradient at 4% opacity
- Noise grain: a fixed pseudo-element using an SVG filter or CSS background
- No external UI component libraries — build everything from scratch with Tailwind
- All placeholder links (`href="#"`) clearly commented for where real links go
- Demo link opens in new tab — placeholder `href="#demo"` with comment
- Mobile responsive — single column layout on screens below 768px, ticker and animations preserved
- No TypeScript errors — use proper types throughout
- Comment each major section clearly for easy navigation

